{"tid":2462027,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"賴冠霖「挺新疆棉」切割愛牌NIKE、Converse！　趕飛機急換穿拖鞋","createTime":"2021-03-25T17:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T20:37:10.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d6b6f861b2092fe119cd6cb1b00ac7010a0ec9","tid":2462027,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5527/d5527838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5527%2Fd5527838.jpg&h=cd35f19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaNm6MSs2arrv3Wqe838gJC9CbBJCwnqzsLEN3oU9E1E4?filename=ex0mXPk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fex0mXPk.png&h=1ad32477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多家知名國際品牌H&amp;M、NIKE、Converse等，因拒用新疆棉花，並稱新疆有「強迫勞動」情況，遭到大陸民間強烈抵制。為此，不少大陸藝人都火速站出來與相關品牌解約、切割，其中賴冠霖不但在微博轉發了支持新疆棉花的貼文，還被發現緊急換掉了前兩天穿的爭議品牌鞋子，索性穿拖鞋出現在機場。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有眼尖粉絲發現賴冠霖23日現身機場時，腳上穿的是Converse的帆布鞋，昨天（24日）在錄製《快樂大本營》穿的則是NIKE球鞋，今日再度前往機場趕行程時，由於新疆棉花事件已經延燒開來，他也被目擊到乾脆換上拖鞋。根據粉絲說法，NIKE、Converse都是他先前經常穿的愛牌。<br />\n<br />\n賴冠霖25日也在微博轉發了官媒《人民日報》的貼文，並在內文加上話題標籤「我支持新疆棉花」，獲得大陸網友讚賞「蠻好的，立場很堅定！」、「用行動證明！」、「笑死我啦強大的求生欲」，但也有粉絲跳出來表示他本來就喜歡穿拖鞋，不需要過度解讀。"},{"pid":"dfb4731ffbca2727e00304779a2408785414fbf0","tid":2462027,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1946523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1946523&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gr%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=c0b01e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1946523</a>"},{"pid":"9cfd0d4b526bd04241b8129c53fcdba9711d8171","tid":2462027,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"361李寧牌喬丹體育，機會嚟啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\